  "original_title": "Sajith takes a step back",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sajith takes a step back",
      "author": "Thilina Walpola",
      "body_lines": [
        "For\u00a0 once\u00a0\u00a0 our\u00a0 political\u00a0 leaders\u00a0\u00a0 have\u00a0 shown\u00a0 leadership\u00a0 qualities. Sajith\u00a0 has\u00a0 to\u00a0 be praised and garlanded for\u00a0 taking\u00a0 a\u00a0\u00a0 step\u00a0 back\u00a0 and\u00a0 conceding the the ticket to\u00a0 Dullas to ensure a better chance of dethroning the acting incumbent.It\u00a0 was\u00a0 a\u00a0 patriotic\u00a0 and\u00a0 selfless\u00a0 act rarely\u00a0 seen\u00a0\u00a0 among\u00a0 politicians\u00a0 today. If\u00a0 we\u00a0 can\u00a0 elect\u00a0 a\u00a0 president\u00a0 from\u00a0 among our MPs\u00a0 without\u00a0 rancor, dissent and\u00a0 unity\u00a0 of\u00a0 purpose,\u00a0 we have certainly come\u00a0 of\u00a0 age.",
        "We\u00a0 have\u00a0 reached\u00a0 the\u00a0 depths\u00a0 of\u00a0 despair with\u00a0 no\u00a0 money,\u00a0 no\u00a0 friends,\u00a0 no\u00a0 gas and no\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 petrol.\u00a0 We\u00a0 only\u00a0 have\u00a0 each\u00a0 other. So unity\u00a0 is\u00a0 the\u00a0 need\u00a0 of\u00a0 the\u00a0 hour. United\u00a0 we\u00a0 stand and divided\u00a0 we\u00a0 fall. As this is written, we don\u2019t know\u00a0 what\u00a0 kind\u00a0 of\u00a0 fruit Sajith\u2019s noble gesture will\u00a0 bear.\u00a0 Ours\u00a0 is\u00a0 not\u00a0 to\u00a0 see\u00a0 the\u00a0 future. We\u00a0 can\u00a0 only\u00a0 hope\u00a0 good\u00a0 actions\u00a0 will\u00a0 give\u00a0 good\u00a0 results.",
        "This\u00a0 reminds\u00a0 me\u00a0 of\u00a0 something\u00a0 I\u00a0 read during\u00a0 India\u2019s\u00a0 struggle\u00a0 for\u00a0 Independence. Jinnah\u00a0 who\u00a0 fought\u00a0 side\u00a0 by\u00a0 side\u00a0 with\u00a0 Gandhi\u00a0 and\u00a0 Nehru to win independence,\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 made\u00a0 a\u00a0 bid\u00a0 for\u00a0 the\u00a0 premiership and\u00a0 Nehru, the\u00a0\u00a0 legitimate\u00a0 aspirant\u00a0 and\u00a0 true\u00a0 patriot, agreed\u00a0 to\u00a0 step aside. The\u00a0 Congress\u00a0 Party\u00a0 howled\u00a0 and the\u00a0 protest\u00a0 prevailed.\u00a0 The\u00a0 rest\u00a0 is\u00a0 history.Sajith, you\u00a0 have shown the way.",
        "UN to host over 190 world leaders and delegates \u2014 Despite threats from deadly new Covid-19 variant",
